Package: vpn
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: vpncli <vpncli@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/vpncli/vpn
Description: Intuitive xray VPN manager
 vpn drives xray from a friendly CLI/TUI: add servers from vless://
 share links, switch between them, and shape routing with simple presets
 (e.g. .ru domains bypass the VPN). The binary is self-contained; it only
 needs the `xray` engine installed separately.
